            "title": "「幣圈」危機!︱法國加密幣平台創辦人女兒  巴黎街頭險被擄今年第3宗︱有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/0fa6508f819490cfb40fc01746c89304/2025-05/New_Project_1554.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/00fc42c1312c71f0bffd4177d1c00102/86358f3174cc4295a0924baaa799761b-7738ce260f889e317205019fba99dc79-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-682547e538103\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-682547e538105\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"路人（紅圈）用滅火器作武器，成功驅走企圖綁架的匪徒。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c79d2a2c0d2de01f9c1bc5badc5cb5e7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051509434797984.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">路人（紅圈）用滅火器作武器，成功驅走企圖綁架的匪徒。Ｘ@GilbertCollard</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>法國再爆涉及加密貨幣富豪的綁架案。法國知名加密貨幣交易所Paymium的CEO Pierre Noizat的女兒及其外孫在巴黎街頭，被人企圖擄走，幸途人拯救才未被綁架。法國今年已發生最少3宗涉及加密貨幣圈的綁架勒索案。法國內政部部長計劃與加密貨幣業界人士會晤，商討防範方法。\n\n</p><h2>勇途人滅火筒救人</h2>\n<p>據法媒《巴黎人報》、法國24台等報道，13日在巴黎第11區街頭，一輛白色客貨車上的3名蒙面男子，企圖將正在散步的Pierre Noizat的女兒和外孫捉上車擄走。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"匪徒企圖當街擄走人質。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08829ea235f638decc0e2c02d336b56f/2025-05/2156526.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        匪徒企圖當街擄走人質。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"有途人取出滅火筒衝向匪徒。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ea4cd051b4d62aa0b245d7ca12f1ccf/2025-05/B_52656.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有途人取出滅火筒衝向匪徒。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"有途人取出滅火筒衝向匪徒。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/73c1eaaf05def168291f2cab28432af3/2025-05/C_455.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有途人取出滅火筒衝向匪徒。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"途人成功逼退匪徒，再用滅火筒擲向逃走匪徒的車輛。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4ad68357b5ece9e748b0b235a6b9035b/2025-05/D_4898954.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        途人成功逼退匪徒，再用滅火筒擲向逃走匪徒的車輛。Ｘ@GilbertCollard\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"途人安慰險被綁走的受害人。@GilbertCollard\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ced03f49fcb86cf54b739b8ecf2b5b7/2025-05/E_897895.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        途人安慰險被綁走的受害人。@GilbertCollard\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3452792/%E9%8B%BC%E9%90%B5%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B%E9%81%AD%E6%92%95%E7%A5%A8%E8%8F%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%87%B8%E7%B4%85%E5%80%8D%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3138%E8%90%AC-%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D26%E6%AD%B2%E5%9C%A8%E9%80%83%E6%B9%96%E5%8D%97%E5%A5%B3\">鋼鐵大王遭撕票︱菲警懸紅倍增至$138萬 通緝26歲在逃湖南女</a>\n</p>\n<p>二人與匪徒發生糾纏，期間有途人挺身而出，取起滅火筒作勢攻擊匪徒，迫使綁匪逃走，成功阻止Pierre Noizat的家人被綁走。\n\n</p>\n<p>這已是今年起碼第3宗法國涉及加密貨幣業界的綁架或企圖綁架案。5月初，巴黎警方解救了一位加密貨幣企業家的父親，該受害者因與一起涉及700萬歐元（780萬美元）的綁架陰謀有關而被囚禁數日及切去一根手指。\n\n</p><h2>今年已3宗涉幣圈綁架案</h2>\n<p>今年年初，知名加密硬體錢包製造商Ledger的聯合創始人David Balland在法國中部住所被綁架。他被劫持直至1月22日晚，警方通過專項行動成功將其解救。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3455271/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AF%8C%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%81%E6%9E%B6%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85-%E8%AD%A6%E6%95%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%AD%E8%87%AA%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%AA%E6%BC%94%E8%A9%90%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D\">中國富二代在大馬遭綁架虐待？ 警「救人」揭自導自演詐父母</a>\n</p>\n<p>面對針對加密貨幣界的富豪綁架勒索案，法國內政部長Bruno Retailleau已邀請業界會面，研究加強安全問題。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
